\f0\b\fs40 \cf2 Recoupable World-Building\
\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\sl324\slmult1\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs30 \cf2 What is Recoupable?
\f1\b0\fs24 \
Recoupable is building the new music industry. A world where humans do what they love, and AI agents handle the rest. Our current ICP is music SMB c-suite, mainly CEOs, who want to make sure their company does not die. Our future ICP is independent creatives, and the 100M new music makers who will suddenly be able to create songs, but have no way to monetize them. Recoupable is the Shepard for both. When you think AI music business, you think Recoupable. \
\

\f0\b\fs30 What is Recoupable brand universe?
\f1\b0\fs24 \
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\sl324\slmult1\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
We DO NOT want to be a sterile software company. We want to live at the intersection of a record label that helps creatives transcend into pop culture, AI infrastructure and education, and creative freedom. The Recoupable brand universe is set in a near-future creative urban city where nature and technology are woven together so seamlessly that neither dominates. Glass towers breathe with rooftop gardens and climbing vines, plazas are shaded by flowering trees, and quiet parks open like courtyards between lived-in streets. The city feels utopian without being sterile \'97 bustling, warm, and deeply human. People laugh, trade, sketch, share tea, and play music; small, slightly worn robots pad through the same spaces with expressive curiosity. Atmosphere and light do most of the storytelling: soft daylight, painterly haze, and gentle bloom hold everything in a dreamlike but grounded mood. The visual logic is semi-anime, semi-realistic painterly realism \'97 fine surface detail where it matters (faces, hands, fabric folds, scuffs on robots), with watercolor-like gradients and the kind of atmospheric perspective you\'92d expect from Ghibli/Shinkai backgrounds, minus any slide into cel-shaded cartoon or hyper-CGI shine.\
